. Distribution. Antigua , Bahamas , Barbados , Bequia, Cuba , Dominica , Grand Cayman, Guana, Grenada , Guadeloupe, Hispaniola, Jamaica , Martinique, Mustique, St. Croix, St. Lucia, St. Thomas, St. Vincent, Union. The subspecies L. a .
